  "title": "Technical Sales (Own Car) | Petrochemical | Oil & Gas | Shipyard",
  "description": "<ul><li><p><strong>Role: Outdoor Sales Engineer</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Working Hours: 8.15am - 5.30pm</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Working Days: 5 Days [Monday - Friday]</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Location: Gul Crescent / Joo Koon, Singapore</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Basic Salary: $3,000 - $4,000 + $70 Phone Allowance + 14 Days AL</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Entitled to $1020 (transport allowance) + AWS + Yearly Commission </strong></p></li></ul><p><em><strong>Summary: Sales Engineer role in the Water Jetting & Industrial Cleaning division under the Sales Department, preferable exposure from petrochemical, oil refinery, shipyard, oil & gas industries.</strong></em></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ol><li><p>Polytechnic Diploma or equivalent; preferably in a business associated or engineering related field</p></li><li><p>Experienced in corporate / industrial sales, especially in the oil and gas , petrochemical, oil refinery, shipyard settings.</p></li><li><p>Holding a Class 3 driving license and own a car</p></li></ol><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Serve existing assigned accounts and prospect potential new customers</p></li><li><p>Learn & familiarize our products well, understand users’ needs, and so be able to offer solutions and assistance to meet their requirements</p></li><li><p>Perform hands-on product demonstrations, as well as occasionally conduct presentations to mid-size audiences including management levels</p></li></ul><p></p><p>#SCR-carson-cheong</p><p>⭕ Cheong Kar Chun ⭕ Team Manager ⭕ R1980386</p><p>⭕ The Supreme HR Advisory ⭕ 14C7279</p>",
